# 03 - Code Review
# Analyze code files and provide feedback

NAME code-review
INPUT path
INPUT language DEFAULT "auto-detect"

GOAL scan "Use glob to find source files in $path. Read only key files (max 5). Identify $language if auto-detect."
GOAL review "Review for top 3-5 issues: prioritize bugs and security over style. Be specific."
GOAL suggest "List top 5 actionable improvements. Brief code examples only if essential. Save to code-review-output.md."

RUN review_flow USING scan, review, suggest
